AND (&)
- all 1's -> 1
- any 0's -> 0

OR (|)
- all 0's -> 0
- any 1's -> 1

XOR (^)
- even 1's -> 0
- odd 1's  -> 1

NOT (!)
- 1 -> 0
- 0-> 1

Right Shift Operation (>>)
- a=5, binary(101)  a>>1 (1 right bit will go off)
    =10 
- a=10, binary(1010) a>>3 (3 right bit will go off)
    =1 (10/2,5/2, 2/2 =1)

